metadata.name: Orchid, that is not
metadata.description:
The project "Orchid, that is not" as a symbol of concern for the protection of endangered species.
The current trend towards the abolition of protected areas and the development of these territories by people will lead to serious environmental disasters.

The “Orchid, that is not” project is aimed at preserving rare species of endangered animals and plants, our decoration and NFT token as a symbol that it is time to think about the planet, because the Earth has many “eyes” and forces with which it is so easy to reach humanity.

We donate 20% of the sale of "Orchid, that is not" to the global organization WWF for the conservation of endangered species.
